  "instructions": "Now that you know how Phrasal Verbs work, let's learn some new ones! Native speakers almost never use big dictionary words for everyday actions. They use these small 2-word combinations instead. Memorize these 15 essential Phrasal Verbs.",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "note",
      "text": "For example, instead of saying 'I will discard the trash' (very robotic), native speakers say 'I will throw away the trash'."
    }
  ],
